professional_summary.label: Professional Summary
professional_summary.sourceData: A graduated student of BA (Hons) in English for Business and Professional Communication in PolyU with experience in Administrative/ Customer Service and Influencer management at well-known MNC, Local Fashion Company, and luxury e-commerce start-up. Experienced on social media platforms such as Facebook, Instagram, and YouTube. Comfortable working with a team and independently in a fast paced environment. Effective communicator with a creative mind and keen attention for detail. Willing to learn and seeking opportunities to participate in the Fashion & Beauty industry with passion.
